"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"The US president accused Iran of doing a very poor job with the waterway and said Tehran better not be charging fees to oil tankers. Both sides have reason to end the war but share no common ground.\",            \"english_title\": \"US President Criticizes Iran\",            \"translated_version\": \"El presidente de EE.UU. acus\u00f3 a Ir\u00e1n de hacer un mal trabajo con el canal y dijo que Teher\u00e1n no deber\u00eda cobrar a los barcos de petr\u00f3leo. Ambos lados quieren terminar la guerra pero no est\u00e1n de acuerdo.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Presidente de EE.UU. Critica a Ir\u00e1n\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The Israeli military claims Mohammed Wishah was a Hamas terrorist, which the Qatar-based network has previously denied.\",            \"english_title\": \"Israeli Military and Mohammed Wishah\",            \"translated_version\": \"El ej\u00e9rcito de Israel dice que Mohammed Wishah era un terrorista de Hamas, pero la red de Qatar lo ha negado antes.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Ej\u00e9rcito de Israel y Mohammed Wishah\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Trump has given priority to Afrikaners, a white minority group he says is being persecuted. South Africa has objected to his characterisation.\",            \"english_title\": \"Trump and Afrikaners\",            \"translated_version\": \"Trump ha dado prioridad a los Afrikaners, un grupo blanco que \u00e9l dice est\u00e1 siendo perseguido. Sud\u00e1frica no est\u00e1 de acuerdo con lo que \u00e9l dice.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Trump y Afrikaners\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Vladimir Putin announced the truce, which will last from Saturday afternoon on 11 April through Easter Sunday. Lebanese officials had called for a ceasefire before talks begin.\",            \"english_title\": \"Putin Announces Truce\",            \"translated_version\": \"Vladimir Putin anunci\u00f3 la tregua, que durar\u00e1 desde la tarde del s\u00e1bado 11 de abril hasta el domingo de Pascua. Los oficiales libaneses pidieron un alto al fuego antes de empezar las conversaciones.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Putin Anuncia Tregua\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The US president says Nato wasn't there when we needed them during the Iran war.\",            \"english_title\": \"US President on Nato\",            \"translated_version\": \"El presidente de EE.UU. dice que la OTAN no estuvo cuando los necesit\u00e1bamos durante la guerra con Ir\u00e1n.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Presidente de EE.UU. sobre la OTAN\"        }    ]}"